Blend @blå druer{1%kilo} and #strainer{} to sort seeds from the must. Cut @stor kylling{1} into 8 pieces. Chop @stort løg{1}. In a #pot{}, brown the chicken and the onion in @olie{}. Add @lille glas rødvin{1} and #reduce{} slightly. Pour in the #grape must{} created earlier. Add coarsely chopped @store tomater{4} and chopped @fed hvidløg{3-4}. Simmer ~{45%minutes}. Remove chicken pieces. #Blend{} the sauce and season with @salt{} and @peber{}. Bring to a boil. Return chicken to the sauce. Serve with strips of @store Karl Johan svampe{4}, fried over #high heat{}, chopped @potte persille{1} and @fløde{}.